id: pm-qpus
title: Add schema show-status status inspection
description: "Add a first-class pm schema show-status subcommand so agents can inspect one resolved status definition (id, roles, aliases, source, description, order) without parsing full schema lists."
type: Feature
status: in_progress
priority: 2
tags[3]: agent-ux,"area:schema",pm-cli
created_at: "2026-06-07T07:18:14.259Z"
updated_at: "2026-06-07T07:55:14.792Z"
assignee: codex-schema-show-status-20260607
author: codex-schema-show-status-20260607
parent: pm-8jdc
comments[4]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-06-07T07:18:19.263Z",codex-schema-show-status-20260607,"Kickoff: duplicate check complete (pm search \"schema show-status status inspection\" + pm list-open --parent pm-8jdc) found no active equivalent child item. Starting implementation for status-level schema inspection with CLI/MCP/contracts/tests/docs parity."
  "2026-06-07T07:55:00.184Z",codex-schema-show-status-20260607,"Implementation complete: added pm schema show-status end-to-end across CLI runtime/dispatch, MCP pm_run schema action, contract metadata, and docs/tests. New schema subcommand behavior resolves status aliases, returns builtin/custom source, roles, aliases, description/order in JSON, and human-readable output via formatSchemaShowStatusHuman. Updated command discovery/help strings and regenerated contracts fixture after action contract changes."
  "2026-06-07T07:55:00.510Z",codex-schema-show-status-20260607,"Verification evidence: pnpm build; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/schema-command.spec.ts tests/unit/contracts-command.spec.ts tests/integration/mcp-handshake.spec.ts (55 passed); pnpm contracts:update + pnpm contracts:check; pnpm changelog:pm + pnpm changelog:pm:check; pnpm release:gates (2540 tests, 100% coverage, static/docs/security/smoke gates passed). Manual temp-dir smoke passed at /tmp/tmp.EWFMSbmb1D using node dist/cli.js: init -> schema add-status review -> schema show-status review/in_review/open -> create+update status -> schema remove-status review -> show-status review expected unknown_status failure -> schema show Task."
  "2026-06-07T07:55:00.828Z",codex-schema-show-status-20260607,"GitHub/Sentry triage 2026-06-07: gh issue list open = none, gh pr list open = none, dependabot/code-scanning/secret-scanning open alerts all empty ([]). Sentry telemetry gate passed in best-effort mode: critical=0, high=0, finish_error_rate_pct=1.88, missing_error_code_rows=0. Dependency review: commander 15 remains blocked by engines (node >=22.12) while repo supports node >=20. Updated managed pm-changelog extension to latest available npm version 2026.6.7 during changelog verification."
